&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;The outer pipes (&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;text-align:center&#34;&gt;) are optional, and you don&#39;t need to make the raw Markdown line up prettily. You can also use inline Markdown.&lt;/td&gt;
